## DNS Record Updates

### A Records
```bash
# Update A records for web services
az network dns record-set a add-record \
  --resource-group {{ resource_group }} \
  --zone-name {{ dns_zone | default('example.com') }} \
  --record-set-name www-{{ region }} \
  --ipv4-address {{ web_ip | default('10.0.1.10') }}

# Update A records for API endpoints
az network dns record-set a add-record \
  --resource-group {{ resource_group }} \
  --zone-name {{ dns_zone | default('example.com') }} \
  --record-set-name api-{{ region }} \
  --ipv4-address {{ api_ip | default('10.0.1.20') }}
```

### CNAME Records
```bash
# Update CNAME for regional services
az network dns record-set cname set-record \
  --resource-group {{ resource_group }} \
  --zone-name {{ dns_zone | default('example.com') }} \
  --record-set-name {{ region }}-service \
  --cname {{ region }}.internal.example.com
```

